            <paragraph>The following example deletes all sessions belonging to user <code>chef123</code> in database named <code>cookbook</code>.</paragraph>
            
            <paragraph><strong>Request</strong></paragraph>
            
<code-block>
DELETE /cookbook/_user/chef123/_session HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:59840
</code-block>
            
